			<p class="double-margin--bottom">Talent Cloud uses a 1.333 type scale for its typography.</p>

			<h1 class="margin--bottom">H1: Thin, <span class="bold">Bold</span>, <span class="crimson">Coloured</span></h1>

			<h2 class="margin--bottom">H2: Thin, <span class="bold">Bold</span>, <span class="crimson">Coloured</span></h2>

			<h3 class="margin--bottom">H3: Thin, <span class="bold">Bold</span>, <span class="crimson">Coloured</span></h3>

			<h4 class="margin--bottom">H4: Thin, <span class="bold">Bold</span>, <span class="crimson">Coloured</span></h4>

			<h5 class="double-margin--bottom">H5: Thin, <span class="bold">Bold</span>, <span class="crimson">Coloured</span></h5>

			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis vitae felis at purus molestie luctus. Duis maximus magna ante, id pellentesque purus vestibulum vel. Aliquam erat volutpat. Aliquam mattis turpis a ligula blandit gravida. Fusce lobortis tempus augue quis venenatis. Proin sed lobortis purus. Donec vitae libero id lectus ultrices dignissim convallis ut augue. Etiam imperdiet tellus at dictum molestie. Duis ex dolor, cursus a quam at, vulputate consequat ante. Maecenas vel risus at ante ornare aliquam. Proin risus mi, pellentesque sit amet rhoncus eu, rutrum non ipsum. Praesent cursus fringilla eros, euismod tincidunt dolor rutrum sed. Phasellus tristique non tortor vitae varius. Nam in vestibulum est, ut volutpat urna. Mauris eu vehicula justo, pretium vulputate purus.</p>

		</div>

	{# Forms #}

		<div class="container--layout triple-padding--top">

			<h2 class="center margin--bottom">Forms</h2>

			<hr>

		</div>

		<div class="container--copy double-padding--top">

			<p class="margin--bottom">Our forms require...</p>

			<div class="button-grid center padding--bottom">

				<button
					class="button--outline--plum"
					type="button">
					Submit
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--solid--plum"
					type="button">
					Submit
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--outline--wine"
					type="button">
					Option
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--solid--wine"
					type="button">
					Option
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--outline--crimson"
					type="button">
					Cancel
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--solid--crimson"
					type="button">
					Cancel
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--outline--sunrise"
					type="button">
					Click Here
				</button>

				<button
					class="button--solid--sunrise"
					type="button">
					Click Here
				</button>

			</div>

			<form>

				{# Form Error #}

					<div class="error">

						<img src="/images/icons/exclamation-circle-crimson.svg" alt="Error Icon">

						<span>Uh oh! These credentials don't seem to match our records.</span>

					</div>

				{# Form Alert #}

					<div class="alert">

						<img src="/images/icons/notification-plum.svg" alt="Error Icon">

						<span>Heads up! We wanted to let you know that there is important information on this page.</span>

					</div>

				{# Form Elements #}

					<div class="flex-grid gutter">

						<div class="box b-full tl-1of2 input">

							<label>My Name</label>

							<span class="required-label">Required</span>

							<div class="input-wrapper">

								<input
									placeholder="e.g. Clark Kent"
									required
									type="text"/>

								<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

							</div>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full tl-1of2 input invalid">

							<label>My Name</label>

							<span class="required-label">Required</span>

							<div class="input-wrapper">

								<input
									placeholder="e.g. Diana Prince"
									required
									type="text"/>

								<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

							</div>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full input">

							<label>My Story</label>

							<span class="required-label">Required</span>

							<div class="input-wrapper">

								<textarea
									placeholder="e.g. One day Bruce Wayne..."
									required>I am Batman.</textarea>

								<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

							</div>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full copy">

							<p>This is an example of paragraph text inside of a form. This type of text can be used for instructional or contextual purposes.</p>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full input">

							<label>Select Your Partner</label>

							<span class="required-label">Required</span>

							<div class="input-wrapper">

								<div
									class="select">

									<img src="/images/icons/chevron-down.svg" alt="Dropdown Chevron">

									<select>

										<option>Aquaman</option>
										<option>Martian Manhunter</option>
										<option>Booster Gold</option>
										<option>The Flash</option>

									</select>

								</div>

								<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

							</div>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full tl-1of2 input">

							<label>Today's Date</label>

							<span class="required-label">Required</span>

							<div class="input-wrapper">

								<input
									type="date"/>

								<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

							</div>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full tl-1of2 input">

							<label>Your Password</label>

							<span class="required-label">Required</span>

							<div class="input-wrapper">

								<div class="password">

									<input
										id=""
										required
										type="password"
										value="G1assesAreTheBestDisguise"/>

									<button type="button">
										<img src="/images/icons/eye.svg" alt="Show/Hide Password">
									</button>

								</div>

								<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

							</div>

						</div>

					</div>

				{# Fieldset Example #}

					<fieldset>

						<div class="flex-grid gutter">

							<legend class="box b-full">
								Fieldset Information
							</legend>

							<div class="box b-full copy">

								<p>This is an example of paragraph text inside of a form. This type of text can be used for instructional or contextual purposes.</p>

							</div>

                            {# Radio Selection #}

    							<div class="box b-full input">

    								<label>Select Your Level</label>

    								<span class="required-label">Required</span>

    								<div class="input-wrapper">

    									<div 
    										aria-orientation="horizontal"
    										class="radio-group flex-grid"
    										role="radiogroup">

    										<label 
    											class="box b-full tp-1of4"
    											for="r1">

    											<input
    												id="r1"
    												name="sample-radio-group"
    												type="radio"
    												checked />

    											<span>Beginner</span>

    										</label>

    										<label 
    											class="box b-full tp-1of4"
    											for="r2">

    											<input
    												id="r2"
    												name="sample-radio-group"
    												type="radio" />

    											<span>Intermediate</span>

    										</label>

    										<label 
    											class="box b-full tp-1of4"
    											for="r3">

    											<input
    												id="r3"
    												name="sample-radio-group"
    												type="radio" />

    											<span>Advanced</span>

    										</label>

    										<label 
    											class="box b-full tp-1of4"
    											for="r4">

    											<input
    												id="r4"
    												name="sample-radio-group"
    												type="radio" />

    											<span>Lead</span>

    										</label>

    									</div>

    									<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

    								</div>

    							</div>

							{# Checkbox List #}

								<div class="box b-full input">

                                    <label>I want the following superpowers:</label>

                                    <span class="required-label">Required</span>

                                    <div class="input-wrapper">

                                        <div class="checkbox-group flex-grid gutter">

                                            <label 
                                                class="box b-1of2 tl-1of3 dl-1of4"
                                                for="c1">

                                                <input
                                                    id="c1"
                                                    type="checkbox" />

                                                    <span>Flight</span>

                                            </label>

                                            <label 
                                                class="box b-1of2 tl-1of3 dl-1of4"
                                                for="c2">

                                                <input
                                                    id="c2"
                                                    type="checkbox" />

                                                    <span>Strength</span>

                                            </label>

                                            <label 
                                                class="box b-1of2 tl-1of3 dl-1of4"
                                                for="c3">

                                                <input
                                                    id="c3"
                                                    type="checkbox" />

                                                    <span>Laser Vision</span>

                                            </label>

                                            <label 
                                                class="box b-1of2 tl-1of3 dl-1of4"
                                                for="c4">

                                                <input
                                                    id="c4"
                                                    type="checkbox" />

                                                    <span>Invulnerability</span>

                                            </label>

                                            <label 
                                                class="box b-1of2 tl-1of3 dl-1of4"
                                                for="c5">

                                                <input
                                                    id="c5"
                                                    type="checkbox" />

                                                    <span>Telekinesis</span>

                                            </label>

                                        </div>

                                        <span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

                                    </div>

								</div>

							{# Input (Number) #}

								<div class="box b-full tl-1of3 input">

									<label># of Sidekicks</label>

									<span class="required-label">Required</span>

									<div class="input-wrapper">

										<input
											placeholder="0"
											required
											type="number"/>

										<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

									</div>

								</div>

							{# Input (URL) #}

								<div class="box b-full tl-2of3 input">

									<label>My Website</label>

									<span class="required-label">Required</span>

									<div class="input-wrapper">

										<input
											placeholder="e.g. http://talent.canada.ca"
											required
											type="url"/>

										<span class="error-copy">This input has an error or is formatted incorrectly.</span>

									</div>

								</div>

						</div>

					</fieldset>

				{# Form Actions #}

					<div class="flex-grid gutter actions">

						<div class="box b-full pl-1of2">

							<button
								class="button--outline--crimson"
								type="button">
								Cancel
							</button>

						</div>

						<div class="box b-full pl-1of2">

							<button
								class="button--solid--plum"
								type="button">
								Submit
							</button>

						</div>

					</div>

			</form>

		</div>

    {# Common Elements #}

		<div class="container--layout triple-padding--top">

			<h2 class="center margin--bottom">Common Elements</h2>

			<hr>

            <div class="flex-grid gutter double-padding--top">

                <div class="box b-full tp-1of2 dm-1of3 card job-summary">

                    <div class="heading">

                    </div>

                    <div class="application-date">

                    </div>

                    <div class="summary flex-grid gutter">

                        <div class="box b-full pl-1of2">

                            <span class="half-margin--bottom block crimson bold">
                                Location
                            </span>

                            <span class="summary-copy">
                                Ottawa, Ontario
                            </span>

                        </div>

                        <div class="box b-full pl-1of2">

                            <span class="half-margin--bottom block crimson bold">
                                Annual Salary
                            </span>

                            <span>
                                $67,000 - $90,000
                            </span>

                        </div>

                        <div class="box b-full">

                            <span class="half-margin--bottom block crimson bold">
                                Impact
                            </span>

                            <span>
                                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec varius fringilla metus id rutrum. Fusce condimentum risus ut purus consequat tempor. Proin vestibulum in nunc vel iaculis. Vivamus accumsan volutpat ligula, et accumsan tellus porttitor id. Donec vitae leo pretium, interdum elit in, scelerisque nibh.
                            </span>

                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

		</div>

{% endblock %}